EX-EASTENDER Hannah Waterman yesterday married former co-star Ricky Groves.

Hannah (Laura Beale) and Ricky (mechanic Garry Hobbs) wed in a country church on Dartmoor.

Several EastEnders stars, including Shane Ritchie and Letitia Dean attended the wedding at Inwardleigh, near Okehampton, Devon.

Hannah, 31, daughter of Minder star Dennis Waterman and his ex-wife Patricia Maynard, 64, met Ricky, 35, when their characters had a fling on the show.

The couple kept their off-screen relationship secret for months but got engaged last year.

Before the wedding, Hannah said: "I couldn't think of anything nicer than confirming how I feel about the man I love."
